睡眠模式”：联动小爱触屏音箱或小米吸顶灯，可实现清晨窗帘开启后音乐响起、晚间关闭窗帘后灯光缓灭等功能。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="3129" src="https://img30.360buyimg.com/sku/jfs/t1/44607/29/27348/169939/6507b644Fdc495d1d/3965145e34f212c3.jpg" title="伸缩轨道 + 免费安装：小米米家智能窗帘 361 元破冰新低（上市 599 元）" width="750" /></p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/KO99FQH" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="740" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/cb8467c9-8abf-4f5b-886e-20a9e9b01364.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="伸缩轨道 + 免费安装：小米米家智能窗帘 361 元破冰新低（上市 599 元）" width="740" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name">米家 智能窗帘伸缩轨道版</span></span><span class="card-abstract"> 1.75-3 米轨道长度</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">多重优惠 361.6 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p>2024 年 11.11 大促全网好价合集：<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fcontentlist%3Fapi%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fnapi.ithome.com%252Fapi%252Ftopmenu%252Fgetmenufeeds%252F166%252F0%252Fnone%252F0%26title%3D2024%25E5%258F%258C11%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BF%2583%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E9%2580%2589%26mode%3D0" target="_blank" title="点此查看">点此查看</a></p><p><span class="font-color-red"><strong>京东无门槛红包&nbsp;</strong></span>至高 11111 元：<a href="https://u.jd.com/CaQySbH" target="_blank" title="点此抽今日红包"><strong>点此抽今日红包</strong></a></p><p><span class="font-color-orangered"><strong>天猫无门槛红包&nbsp;</strong></span>至高 24888 元：<strong><a href="https://s.click.taobao.com/w26hFPt" target="_blank">点此抽今日红包</a></strong></p><p><span class="font-color-purple"><strong>唯品会无门槛红包</strong></span> 至高1111元：<a href="https://t.vip.com/VbMVne" target="_blank"><strong>点此抽今日红包</strong></a></p><p><br /></p><p class="ad-tips">广告声明：文内含有的对外跳转链接（包括不限于超链接、二维码、口令等形式），用于传递更多信息，节省甄选时间，结果仅供参考，IT之家所有文章均包含本声明。</p><div class="tagging1">【广告】</div>
